# 💻 Portfolio Website UI (Practice Project)

This is a **Portfolio Website UI** built using **HTML & CSS** as part of my learning journey.

---

## 🚀 About the Project

This project is a frontend design of a developer portfolio website.  
It includes multiple sections like Home, Services, Skills, Projects, Testimonials, and Contact.

The goal of this project was to improve my understanding of:
- Layout design
- Flexbox
- UI/UX structuring
- Clean and modern styling

---

## ✨ Features

- 🎨 Modern and clean UI design  
- 📱 Structured layout with multiple sections  
- ⚡ Smooth hover effects & animations  
- 🧱 Card-based design  
- 📌 Fixed navigation header  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Used

- HTML5  
- CSS3  

